            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "Taman Buaya & Rekreasi Melaka"
          }
        ]
      },
      "description": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "Experience the unique wildlife of Malaysia at the Melaka Crocodile and Recreation Park, a sprawling 13,000 sq.ft local farm nestled in the historic city of Melaka. Immerse yourself in lush greenery and beautiful vegetation as you explore the farm's diverse facilities. Encounter over 100 crocodiles of four different species in their natural habitat, witnessing trainers interact with these fascinating creatures. The park is also home to various other animals, including emus, tortoises, deers, reptiles, racoons, and more. Explore Miniature Malaysia, featuring smaller replicas of iconic buildings, and cool off in the waterpark—an ideal destination for quality family time!"
          }
        ]
      },
      "rating": {
        "average_value": 4.3,
        "rating_count": 100
