          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Terms & Conditions: Admission Tickets are valid on the selected date. The water playground is open to all ages at no additional charge.Eligibility Children aged 4 and below are entitled to free admission. Adult tickets are for individuals aged 13 to 54 years old. Child tickets are for individuals aged 5 to 12 years old. Senior citizens (above 55 years old) must purchase tickets on-site and present a valid Identity Card (IC) at the counter. OKU visitors must buy tickets on-site and present a valid OKU card for a 50% discount. For MY ticket type, please present your MyKad at the counter.Attraction Access The water playground will be open daily and may close in case of rain. This activity is stroller and wheelchair-accessible. Eating and drinking are not allowed in the swimming pool. Please wear appropriate clothing and swimming attire.Additional Information Your safety and that of your family are at your own risk; the park management will not be responsible for any accidents.Important Notes Tickets must be purchased according to the age category and identification requirements stated above."
              }
